data.text:
@KarachiScribes @ZindagiTrust @ShehzadRoy A non-contact infrared thermometer is not a shooting device emitting radiation. It detects heat emanating from the human body in the form of infrared rays and converts it into electricity.
The thermometer processes the electrical signal and gives the reading on the screen.
